### TESTING SCENARIOS

### Scenario A: Check last mass scan for specific workflow
# 1. Get last mass scan info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rekap-remote/last-mass-scan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# 2. Verify with actual data for POSDATA module
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rekap-remote?module_name=POSDATA&limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Scenario B: Compare multiple modules
# Get last mass scan for all modules
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rekap-remote/last-mass-scan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# Then check individual module details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rekap-remote?module_name=INVENTORY&limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Scenario C: Verify cabang-specific scanning
# Get last mass scan
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rekap-remote/last-mass-scan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# Check specific cabang data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rekap-remote?cab=G001&module_name=POSDATA
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

